      <title>图斯克说，波兰应该考虑使用核武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/polish-premier-tusk-to-boost-army-to-half-a-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总理唐纳德·塔斯克（Donald Tusk）表示，他的国家可能寻求核武器，警告说欧洲可能会在未来几年内与俄罗斯面对战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/polish-premier-tusk-to-boost-army-to-half-a-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 13:11:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
